Teri har cheez jannat ae x(2)  Your face is heaven 

Your everything is heaven  Ho tere pair vi jannat ae  

Ho tere sheher vi jannat ae  Ho assi pee jaane ikko saah  

Tere zehar vi jannat ae  Your legs are heaven  

Your city is also heaven  I’ll drink it all in one sip 

Your poison is also heaven  Ho jannat ae teri galliyan 

Teri dehleez jannat ae  Ho jannat ae tera hasna  

Teri har cheez jannat ae  Your streets are heaven  

The threshold (to your house) is also heaven  

Your laughter is heaven  Your everything is heaven  Hoo.. 

Hun tere bin namumkin  Karna guzara ho gaya  

Allah di kasam Allah di kasam  Tu mainu enna pyara ho gaya x(2) 

It has become impossible  To live without you  I swear on Allah

You have become to dear to me  Tera ladna vi jannat ae  Teri tameez jannat ae 

Ho jannat ae tera hasna  Teri har cheez jannat ae  Your fighting (with me?) is also heaven

Your manners are also heaven  Your laughter is heaven  Your everything is heaven 

Ho jannat ae tera hasna  Teri har cheez jannat ae  Your laughter is heaven 

Your everything is heaven  Ho sarheya nahi, mareya nahi  Dupptta tera jinnu chhu gaya  Tu jhummeya si jo parinda kade o

Main sohneya ambar ho gaya x(2) 

Neither lives, not dies  

The one who was touched by your scarf (long scarf)  

You frisk like an independent bird  I’ve become the sky (in which you roam/frisk)  

Teri jhanjhar vi jannat ae  Teri kameez jannat ae  Ho jannat ae tera hasna  

Teri har cheez jannat ae  Your anklet is heaven  Your shirt is heaven  

